Install Mysql and Redis for rails development.

install
=======
install vagrant package from https://www.vagrantup.com/downloads.html

install vagrant plugins:

vagrant plugin install vagrant-omnibus
vagrant plugin install vagrant-berkshelf

add vagrant box:

vagrant box add precise64 http://files.vagrantup.com/precise64.box

cd rails3_development_vagrant_machine
bundle install
vagrant up


In the rails project add the follows lines n the file config/database.yml

base: &base
  adapter: mysql2
  encoding: utf8
  pool: 5
  username: root
  password: 1234
  host: localhost

development:
  database: healthyfoodnow_dev
  <<: *base

test:
  database: healthyfoodnow_test
  <<: *base
